{"tid":2119345,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁君彥：需由政府決定何時及如何舉行選舉","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T04:58:46.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"831c766429f91af45703b814daec7a186bcfc9d1","tid":2119345,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"立法會主席梁君彥回應立法會選舉應否因應疫情押後時表示，選舉何時以及如何進行需由政府決定，基於香港現時的情況，當局需要妥善安排。至於如果押後選舉，任命臨時立法會應對真空期是否可行，梁君彥表示不知道亦未聽聞，無法回答。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539202-20200722.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539202-20200722.htm&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB%2FCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=83ebf544\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539202-20200722.htm&h=b1e86b12\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539202-20200722.htm</a>"}]}